# .mailmap - Fix author attribution for display
# Maps old author names to preferred display name

# Map all commits to "BIND Agent" for consistent branding
BIND Agent <starlightdaemon@proton.me> ABMG Developer <dev@abmg.local>
BIND Agent <starlightdaemon@proton.me> StarlightDaemon <starlightdaemon@proton.me>
